Freeserve PLC, up $15.50 at $72
</P>
<P>
   T-Online, the Internet unit of Deutsche Telekom AG, is
considering launching a bid for a majority stake in Freeserve PLC,
the largest Internet service provider in the United Kingdom, The
Wall Street Journal reported today.
</P>
