   5. ''Road Trip,'' DreamWorks, $13.5 million, 2,631 locations,
$5,138 average, $35.3 million, two weeks.
</P>
<P>
   6. ''Small Time Crooks,'' DreamWorks, $3.9 million, 870
locations, $4,480 average, $8.9 million, two weeks.
</P>
<P>
   7. ''Frequency,'' New Line, $3.6 million, 1,803 locations,
$2,006 average, $35.1 million, five weeks.
</P>
<P>
   8. ''U-571,'' Universal, $3.3 million, 2,044 locations, $1,595
